id: 329
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"Built the M&B Roofing one-page concept in `index.html` with local approved raster assets under `assets/`. Static checks passed for verified contact facts, internal wording, invented claims, raw hex leakage, section targeting, mobile collapse CSS, and LocalBusiness-style schema. Screenshot capture was attempted but Chromium was blocked by the local macOS sandbox.\n\n<artifact identifier=\"mb-roofing-website-concept\" type=\"text/html\" title=\"M&B Roofing Website Concept\">\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>M&amp;B Roofing - Roof restorations in Jamison Town</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"M&amp;B Roofing provides roof restorations, roof repairs, gutters, fascia, down pipes, tile roofing, metal roofing, and fast-response roofing help in Jamison Town and Greater Western Sydney.\" />\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: oklch(96.5% 0.025 76);\n      --surface: oklch(99% 0.011 79);\n      --fg: oklch(24% 0.025 245);\n      --muted: oklch(48% 0.032 66);\n      --border: oklch(88% 0.035 77);\n      --accent: oklch(55% 0.17 35);\n      --on-primary: oklch(100% 0 0);\n      --accent-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 13%, transparent);\n      --fg-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 7%, transparent);\n      --dark-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 88%, var(--muted));\n      --font-display: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-mono: \"SF Mono\", ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace;\n      --fs-h1: clamp(42px, 9vw, 74px);\n      --fs-h2: clamp(30px, 6vw, 48px);\n      --fs-h3: 22px;\n      --fs-lead: 19px;\n      --fs-body: 16px;\n      --fs-meta: 13px;\n      --gap-xs: 8px;\n      --gap-sm: 12px;\n      --gap-md: 20px;\n      --gap-lg: 32px;\n      --gap-xl: 56px;\n      --gap-2xl: 96px;\n      --container: 1160px;\n      --gutter: clamp(18px, 5vw, 36px);\n      --radius: 8px;\n      --radius-lg: 16px;\n    }\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      font-size: var(--fs-body);\n      line-height: 1.55;\n      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n    img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }\n    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }\n    button, input, textarea, select { font: inherit; }\n    button { cursor: pointer; }\n    p { text-wrap: pretty; }\n    h1, h2, h3, h4 { text-wrap: balance; }\n    .container { max-width: var(--container); margin-inline: auto; padding-inline: var(--gutter); }\n    .section { padding-block: clamp(48px, 8vw, var(--gap-2xl)); }\n    .section + .section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n    .stack > * + * { margin-top: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row-between { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .grid-1-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .h1, h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h1); line-height: 0.98; letter-spacing: 0; margin: 0; font-weight: 850; }\n    .h2, h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: 0; margin: 0; font-weight: 800; }\n    .h3, h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h3); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0; }\n    .lead { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: 1.55; color: var(--muted); max-width: 58ch; margin: 0; }\n    .eyebrow {\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin: 0 0 var(--gap-md);\n      font-weight: 800;\n    }\n    .meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-meta); color: var(--muted); }\n    .num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n    .topnav {\n      position: sticky;\n      top: 0;\n      z-index: 10;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 92%, transparent);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .topnav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-block: 12px; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .logo { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 850; color: var(--fg); }\n    .logo-mark {\n      width: 48px;\n      height: 34px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      background: var(--fg);\n      display: grid;\n      place-items: center;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      flex: 0 0 auto;\n    }\n    .topnav nav { display: flex; gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .topnav nav a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; }\n    .topnav nav a:hover { color: var(--fg); }\n    .topnav .btn-primary { background: var(--fg); color: var(--on-primary); border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .topnav .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 88%, var(--muted)); }\n    .btn {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 8px;\n      min-height: 44px;\n      padding: 12px 18px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      border: 1px solid transparent;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 850;\n      letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      transition: transform 0.05s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;\n      white-space: nowrap;\n    }\n    .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }\n    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--on-primary); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 86%, var(--fg)); }\n    .btn-secondary { background: var(--surface); color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--border); }\n    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: transparent; padding-inline: 8px; }\n    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-arrow::after { content: \">\"; transition: transform 0.15s ease; }\n    .btn-arrow:hover::after { transform: translateX(2px); }\n    .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 28px; }\n    .card-flat { background: transparent; border: 0; padding: 0; }\n    .feature .feature-mark {\n      width: 38px;\n      height: 38px;\n      display: grid;\n      place-items: center;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      margin-bottom: var(--gap-md);\n      background: var(--surface);\n    }\n    .feature .feature-mark svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }\n    .feature h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; }\n    .feature p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 5px 10px;\n      background: var(--surface);\n      color: var(--muted);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n    }\n    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }\n    .field label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 750; }\n    .input, .textarea, .select {\n      width: 100%;\n      padding: 12px 14px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      background: var(--surface);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font: inherit;\n      font-size: 15px;\n    }\n    .input:focus, .textarea:focus, .select:focus { outline: 3px solid var(--accent-soft); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .textarea { min-height: 108px; resize: vertical; line-height: 1.55; }\n    .hero-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.94fr) minmax(0, 1.06fr); gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: stretch; }\n    .hero-panel {\n      background: var(--fg);\n      color: var(--on-primary);\n      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n      padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 56px);\n      min-height: 620px;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .hero-panel .lead { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--on-primary) 78%, var(--muted)); }\n    .hero-panel .eyebrow { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--on-primary) 68%, var(--muted)); }\n    .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: var(--gap-sm); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px; }\n    .hero-photo {\n      min-height: 620px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      overflow: hidden;\n      position: relative;\n      background: var(--dark-soft);\n    }\n    .hero-photo img, .proof-image img, .material-card img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }\n    .hero-callout {\n      position: absolute;\n      left: 18px;\n      right: 18px;\n      bottom: 18px;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 94%, transparent);\n      border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--border) 72%, transparent);\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      padding: 16px;\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      gap: var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .chip-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 24px; }\n    .service-strip {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n      gap: 1px;\n      background: var(--border);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .service-strip > div { background: var(--surface); padding: 22px; min-height: 158px; }\n    .proof-image {\n      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n      overflow: hidden;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      min-height: 460px;\n      background: var(--surface);\n    }\n    .checklist { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: grid; gap: 12px; }\n    .checklist li { display: flex; gap: 10px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .checklist li::before { content: \"\"; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--accent); flex: 0 0 auto; margin-top: 8px; }\n    .project-teaser {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;\n      gap: var(--gap-lg);\n      align-items: stretch;\n      background: var(--fg);\n      color: var(--on-primary);\n      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .project-teaser > div:first-child { padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px); }\n    .project-teaser .lead { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--on-primary) 75%, var(--muted)); }\n    .materials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-md); padding: var(--gap-md); }\n    .material-card { min-height: 260px; border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--border) 45%, transparent); background: var(--surface); margin: 0; }\n    .steps { counter-reset: step; display: grid; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; }\n    .step { counter-increment: step; background: var(--surface); padding: 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 58px 1fr; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .step::before {\n      content: counter(step, decimal-leading-zero);\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 900;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      border-top: 2px solid var(--accent);\n      padding-top: 8px;\n    }\n    .faq-list { display: grid; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; }\n    details { background: var(--surface); padding: 22px 24px; }\n    summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 850; font-family: var(--font-display); }\n    details p { margin: 12px 0 0; color: var(--muted); max-width: 70ch; }\n    .contact-panel { background: var(--fg); color: var(--on-primary); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: clamp(26px, 5vw, 44px); }\n    .contact-panel .lead, .contact-panel .meta { color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--on-primary) 74%, var(--muted)); }\n    .contact-panel .input, .contact-panel .textarea, .contact-panel .select { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 96%, var(--fg)); }\n    .contact-lines { display: grid; gap: 12px; }\n    .contact-lines a { text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-thickness: 1px; text-underline-offset: 4px; }\n    .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }\n    .pagefoot { padding-block: var(--gap-xl); color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--on-primary) 68%, var(--muted)); font-size: 13px; background: var(--fg); }\n    .pagefoot .row-between { flex-wrap: wrap; }\n    .pagefoot .logo { color: var(--on-primary); }\n    .mobile-phone {\n      position: fixed;\n      left: 16px;\n      right: 16px;\n      bottom: 16px;\n      z-index: 20;\n      display: none;\n      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 20%, transparent);\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 920px) {\n      .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-4, .grid-2-1, .grid-1-2, .hero-split, .project-teaser, .materials { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .topnav nav { display: none; }\n      .topnav .btn { display: none; }\n      .hero-panel, .hero-photo { min-height: auto; }\n      .hero-photo { min-height: 420px; }\n      .service-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .hero-callout { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }\n      .mobile-phone { display: inline-flex; }\n      body { padding-bottom: 76px; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header class=\"topnav\" data-od-id=\"topnav\">\n    <div class=\"container topnav-inner\">\n      <a class=\"logo\" href=\"#top\" aria-label=\"M&amp;B Roofing home\">\n        <span class=\"logo-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 180 48\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n            <path d=\"M9 29 32 10l23 19\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--muted)\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n            <path d=\"M21 28h25v13H21z\" fill=\"var(--surface)\"/>\n            <text x=\"68\" y=\"32\" font-family=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, system-ui, sans-serif\" font-size=\"24\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"var(--surface)\">M&amp;B</text>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n        <span>M&amp;B Roofing</span>\n      </a>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary navigation\">\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#process\">Process</a>\n        <a href=\"#faq\">FAQ</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n      </nav>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"tel:0424371622\">Call 0424 371 622</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"content\">\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"hero\" id=\"top\">\n      <div class=\"container hero-split\">\n        <div class=\"hero-panel\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Jamison Town / Greater Western Sydney</p>\n          <h1>Roof Restorations for Jamison Town / Greater Western Sydney</h1>\n          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">M&amp;B Roofing can present a clear, phone-friendly roofing page with services, trust cues, and a fast quote path for local customers.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"tel:0424371622\">Call for a roof inspection</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#services\">View services</a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"chip-row\" aria-label=\"Common roofing services\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof restorations</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof repairs</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Tile roofing</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Metal roofing</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <figure class=\"hero-photo\" aria-label=\"Roofer working on a metal roof in a residential area\">\n          <img src=\"assets/hero-roofer-metal-roof-wide.png\" alt=\"Roofer working on a metal roof with homes nearby\" />\n          <figcaption class=\"hero-callout\">\n            <span>\n              <strong>Fast quote path</strong><br />\n              <span class=\"meta\">Call or send roof details and M&amp;B Roofing can follow up about the inspection.</span>\n            </span>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#contact\">Send details</a>\n          </figcaption>\n        </figure>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"services\" id=\"services\">\n      <div class=\"container stack\" style=\"gap: 48px;\">\n        <div style=\"max-width: 52ch;\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Services</p>\n          <h2>Roofing help organised around the problem customers can see.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">Start with the visible issue, then use the inspection to separate urgent repairs from broader restoration work.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-strip\">\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"><path d=\"M3 12 12 5l9 7\"/><path d=\"M6 11v8h12v-8\"/></svg></div>\n            <h3>Roof Restorations</h3>\n            <p>For roofs that need cleaning, preparation, repair work, and a clearer path back to presentable condition.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"><path d=\"M5 19 19 5\"/><path d=\"m14 5 5 5\"/><path d=\"m5 14 5 5\"/></svg></div>\n            <h3>Roof Repairs</h3>\n            <p>For leaks, lifted sheets, damaged tiles, flashing concerns, storm wear, and problem areas that need assessment.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"><path d=\"M4 7h16v4a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H8a4 4 0 0 1-4-4Z\"/><path d=\"M8 15v4m8-4v4\"/></svg></div>\n            <h3>Gutters, Fascia And Down Pipes</h3>\n            <p>For roof-edge drainage issues, overflowing gutters, fascia concerns, and down pipe checks.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"><path d=\"M4 17c3-5 7-5 10 0 2 3 4 3 6 0\"/><path d=\"M4 11c3-5 7-5 10 0 2 3 4 3 6 0\"/></svg></div>\n            <h3>Tile And Metal Roofing</h3>\n            <p>Clear service pathways for common residential tile and metal roof needs around Greater Western Sydney.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"><path d=\"M12 3v18M4 8h16M6 16h12\"/></svg></div>\n            <h3>Core Service</h3>\n            <p>A simple contact route for roofing issues that do not fit neatly into one service category.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"><path d=\"m13 2-8 12h7l-1 8 8-12h-7z\"/></svg></div>\n            <h3>Emergency Or Fast Response</h3>\n            <p>A direct phone-first path for urgent roof concerns, storm damage, and time-sensitive inspections.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"proof\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-1-2\">\n        <div class=\"stack\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Trust cues</p>\n          <h2>A clearer first impression for local roofing customers.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\">The page gives homeowners enough structure to act: service area, contact details, roofing services, and a clear inspection-first next step.</p>\n          <ul class=\"checklist\">\n            <li>Verified contact details stay visible and easy to use.</li>\n            <li>Service-area wording keeps the page relevant to Jamison Town and Greater Western Sydney.</li>\n            <li>Inspection-first copy helps customers describe the issue before asking for a quote.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <figure class=\"proof-image\">\n          <img src=\"assets/service-roofer-metal-roof-wide.png\" alt=\"Roofer inspecting a metal roof surface\" />\n        </figure>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"materials\">\n      <div class=\"container project-teaser\">\n        <div class=\"stack\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Local roofing work</p>\n          <h2>Practical roof presentation, not a crowded product catalogue.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\">Material visuals support the main conversion path: understand the roofing issue, contact M&amp;B Roofing, and arrange the next step.</p>\n          <div class=\"chip-row\">\n            <span class=\"tag\">Jamison Town, NSW 2750</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Greater Western Sydney</span>\n            <span class=\"tag\">Roof inspection path</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"materials\">\n          <figure class=\"material-card\"><img src=\"assets/material-standing-seam-front.png\" alt=\"Standing seam metal roof surface\" /></figure>\n          <figure class=\"material-card\"><img src=\"assets/material-standing-seam-symmetric.png\" alt=\"Metal roofing panel detail\" /></figure>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"process\" id=\"process\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2-1\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Process</p>\n          <h2>A simple path from first call to quoted work.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"lead\">The page keeps the next action obvious: call, send roof details, then discuss the practical repair or restoration path before work begins.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"container\" style=\"margin-top: 38px;\">\n        <div class=\"steps\">\n          <div class=\"step\"><div><h3>Call or enquire</h3><p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Use the phone CTA or send a short description of the roof issue.</p></div></div>\n          <div class=\"step\"><div><h3>Describe the roof</h3><p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Share what you can see: leaks, gutters, loose materials, storm damage, or restoration needs.</p></div></div>\n          <div class=\"step\"><div><h3>Inspect and advise</h3><p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Review the visible condition and separate urgent repairs from broader roof improvements.</p></div></div>\n          <div class=\"step\"><div><h3>Quote the work</h3><p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted);\">Give the customer a clearer path before repair or restoration work is booked.</p></div></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"faq\" id=\"faq\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2-1\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">FAQ</p>\n          <h2>Questions homeowners ask before booking.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"faq-list\">\n          <details open>\n            <summary>Do I need a full restoration or a repair?</summary>\n            <p>An inspection can help separate urgent repair work from broader restoration options, so the customer can choose the practical next step.</p>\n          </details>\n          <details>\n            <summary>Can gutters, fascia and down pipes be discussed too?</summary>\n            <p>Yes. The enquiry form includes roof-edge and drainage concerns so those details can be raised with M&amp;B Roofing.</p>\n          </details>\n          <details>\n            <summary>Can I send details before booking?</summary>\n            <p>Yes. Use the form to describe what you can see from the ground, then M&amp;B Roofing can follow up by phone or email.</p>\n          </details>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"contact\" id=\"contact\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2\">\n        <div class=\"contact-panel stack\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Contact</p>\n          <h2>Ready to make the roof easier to understand?</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\">Call for a roof inspection, or send details about the issue and the roof service you need.</p>\n          <div class=\"contact-lines\">\n            <div>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Phone</span>\n              <p style=\"font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 46px); font-weight: 900; margin: 4px 0 0;\" class=\"num\"><a href=\"tel:0424371622\">0424 371 622</a></p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Email</span>\n              <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0;\"><a href=\"mailto:ghilton@live.com.au\">ghilton@live.com.au</a></p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <span class=\"meta\">Location</span>\n              <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0;\">Jamison Town, NSW 2750</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <form class=\"card stack\" action=\"mailto:ghilton@live.com.au\" method=\"post\" enctype=\"text/plain\">\n          <div class=\"form-grid\">\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"name\">Name</label>\n              <input class=\"input\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field\">\n              <label for=\"phone\">Phone</label>\n              <input class=\"input\" id=\"phone\" name=\"phone\" autocomplete=\"tel\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field full\">\n              <label for=\"service\">What do you need help with?</label>\n              <select class=\"select\" id=\"service\" name=\"service\">\n                <option>Roof restoration</option>\n                <option>Roof repairs</option>\n                <option>Gutters, fascia and down pipes</option>\n                <option>Tile and metal roofing</option>\n                <option>Emergency or fast response</option>\n              </select>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"field full\">\n              <label for=\"message\">Roof details</label>\n              <textarea class=\"textarea\" id=\"message\" name=\"message\" aria-label=\"Roof details example: leak near hallway, gutters overflowing, tile damage, metal roof needs a check\"></textarea>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">Send enquiry</button>\n          <p class=\"meta\" style=\"margin: 0;\">You can also call 0424 371 622 for a faster response.</p>\n        </form>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"pagefoot\" data-od-id=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"container row-between\">\n      <a class=\"logo\" href=\"#top\">\n        <span class=\"logo-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 180 48\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n            <path d=\"M9 29 32 10l23 19\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--muted)\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n            <path d=\"M21 28h25v13H21z\" fill=\"var(--surface)\"/>\n            <text x=\"68\" y=\"32\" font-family=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, system-ui, sans-serif\" font-size=\"24\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"var(--surface)\">M&amp;B</text>\n          </svg>\n        </span>\n        <span>M&amp;B Roofing</span>\n      </a>\n      <span class=\"meta\">Roof restorations / Repairs / Gutters / Tile and metal roofing</span>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"tel:0424371622\">Call 0424 371 622</a>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n\n  <a class=\"btn btn-primary mobile-phone\" href=\"tel:0424371622\">Call 0424 371 622</a>\n\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"RoofingContractor\",\n      \"name\": \"M&B Roofing\",\n      \"telephone\": \"0424 371 622\",\n      \"email\": \"ghilton@live.com.au\",\n      \"address\": {\n        \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n        \"addressLocality\": \"Jamison Town\",\n        \"addressRegion\": \"NSW\",\n        \"postalCode\": \"2750\",\n        \"addressCountry\": \"AU\"\n      },\n      \"areaServed\": [\n        \"Jamison Town\",\n        \"Greater Western Sydney\"\n      ],\n      \"serviceType\": [\n        \"Roof Restorations\",\n        \"Roof Repairs\",\n        \"Gutters Fascia And Down Pipes\",\n        \"Tile And Metal Roofing\",\n        \"Emergency Or Fast Response\"\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n</artifact>"}

